      "correctAnswer": "A",
      "explanation": "Forward edge residual capacity = c(e) - f(e), representing unused capacity.",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-18",
      "question": "Ford-Fulkerson worst-case time complexity is:",
      "options": [
        {
